For this branch, I would start with a clean, small implementation:

1. Add aerolit-bundle.yml creation during configure init
2. Make configure init --dry-run show that it would create/update it
3. Make bundle validate validate it when present
4. Keep missing manifest as a warning, not a failure
5. Make doctor continue warning cleanly until the manifest exists
6. Add/adjust your regression test script to check this behavior

Run this first from the repo root on the new branch and send me the output:

